82
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:53,500
It's okay.

83
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:55,980
Whatever you decide to do,
I won't stop you.

84
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:57,900
I just hope you can be safe.

85
